TextEng: Grovelling won't save your worthless hide! Die, dog!
Text: 애원해도 소용없어! 죽어라, 개 같은 놈!

TextEng: You talk do you? Then answer my questions!
Text: 말을 할 줄 알아? 그럼 내 질문에 답해!

TextEng: You beg like dog. Me kill you now.
Text: 너 개처럼 빌어. 나 이제 죽여.

TextEng: Huh? You talk? Then you better answer questions, too!
Text: 응? 너 말해? 그럼 질문에도 답하는 게 좋을 거야!

TextEng: Tell me about your hunting grounds.
Hmm. You tell me 'bout da places you hunt, yuh?
Text: 음. 너 사냥하는 곳 말해줘, 응?

TextEng: Who is this ranger?
Who be this ranger?
Whimpering dog! I've decided to kill you after all.
Text: 징징대는 개 같은 놈! 결국 죽이기로 했어.

TextEng: Me kill you after all, stupid dog!
Text: 나 결국 너 죽여, 멍청한 개!

TextEng: I've got a few more questions.
Me got more questions
That I face you here should be proof that I'm no coward...
Text: 내가 여기 네 앞에 있는 게 겁쟁이가 아니라는 증거야...

TextEng: Would coward have come here to face you? Me no coward.
Text: 겁쟁이가 여기 와서 너 상대하겠어? 나 겁쟁이 아니야.

TextEng: Fine. I want to ask you something else.
Okay, me ask other stuff.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Simply a favor, that's all I ask...
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Jus' an itty-bitty favor, that all me ask...
Where did you learn to talk?
You've been hunting the nearby cattle, haven't you...
How come you talk?
You been hunting da cattle 'round here, yuh?
I need you to stop hunting the cattle... and no people, either!
Text: 가축 사냥 좀 그만해야겠어... 사람도 안 돼!

TextEng: Stop hunting da cows, 'kay? And da people too...
Text: 소 사냥 그만해, 알았지? 사람도 마찬가지고...

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> It sounds like coward's food...
Yes but they're owned by farmers who will have you killed!
Text: 그래, 하지만 농부들 소유야, 그들이 널 죽일 거야!

TextEng: Yuh, but they owned by farmers who kill you!
Text: 응, 하지만 농부들 거야, 그들이 너 죽여!
